{"tid":1251391,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人出現呢種失落感","createTime":"2019-06-22T13:36:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T06:41:41.000Z","uid":18391,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a3c459d60b7e5ff94b3d9afaaf577af211c4515c","tid":1251391,"uid":18391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T13:36:28.000Z","msg":"每次出完去一個人返屋企，一個人生活，一個人碌住連登。<br />\n<br />\n集會既時候團結一齊做一件事好開心。但散去既時候，爭取既野未爭取，屋企面對既就係4面牆，訓又唔安心。<br />\n<br />\n就算今次抗爭成功，我驚自己再唔可以從呢d事抽離返出黎"},{"pid":"c5dc54a0f7b6333dc659c98221a6bb24db3effae","tid":1251391,"uid":46658,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T13:40:14.000Z","msg":"政治係一灘濁水<br />\n一旦你走咗入去就永遠都無法置身事外<br />\n你會發覺呢個社會嘅一切都同政治分唔開<br />\n自然就會灰心 會有無力感 <br />\n會成日問點解呢個世界會係咁？<br />\nYou are not alone bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f82ce32739cbb2bf0728e5413e1921867430126a","tid":1251391,"uid":262290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T13:42:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"973159b9b4f2a133f521d0b4d0aa7776ede39b3b","tid":1251391,"uid":18391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T13:45:43.000Z","msg":"自從烈士出現之後，果種失落感真係好抑鬱"},{"pid":"a471b6f57366fb4dddc05490a529f1a7d24afd68","tid":1251391,"uid":140738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T13:46:29.000Z","msg":"晚晚訓係張床到喊<br />\n<br />\n雖然屋企人都唔支持送中<br />\n<br />\n但個個已經當616嗰日已經贏左<br />\n<br />\n尋晚老母仲要話繼續玩落去就開始煩<br />\n<br />\n要見好就收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n收佢老母咩 <br />\n我地要政府收嗰啲都未收啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkg